  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to prove a reduction of postoperative wound infections after
      direct preoperative use of a microbial sealant in the form of Integuseal for vascular
      procedures on lower extremities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
